   <tag>
      <name>InputSelect</name>
      <tagclass>oracle.jbo.html.jsp.datatags.InputSelectTag</tagclass>
      <bodycontent>empty</bodycontent>
      <info>A Tag to insert an Input select field  to a page. The input select can support single or multiple selections.</info>      
